==Definition==

<b>encomium</b> (<i>noun</i>), plural <b>encomiums</b>
# praise
:M. Le Page Du Pratz, <i>History of Louisisana</i> (PG), p. 39
:: <i>I rejoined our people, and expected a reprimand for having forced the enemy without orders; though I had my excuse ready. But here I was mistaken; for I met with nothing but <b>encomiums</b>.</i>